{"tid":1173844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「百度貼吧」清空2017年前內容     網民：火燒亞歷山大圖書館","createTime":"2019-05-27T11:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T12:58:59.000Z","uid":39464,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5e23c51054b423cc538a72751d24e90805718f41","tid":1173844,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T11:46:17.000Z","msg":"中國熱門線上論壇「百度貼吧」13日無預警清空2017年前內容，引起網民撻伐稱此舉是「火燒亞歷山大圖書館」；陸媒也稱，百度的價值觀把自己打造為「披著科技外衣的網絡營銷公司」。<br />\n<br />\n百度官方13日發出公告，表示為了進行系統升級和維護，2017年1月1日以前的貼文將被隱藏，暫時無法瀏覽；至於何時會恢復，百度並未公布。<br />\n<br />\n微信公眾號「酷玩實驗室」報導稱，有網民將百度此作法對網路文化的影響，比喻為「火燒亞歷山大圖書館」，且「火還是亞歷山大自己放的」。<br />\n<br />\n百度貼吧誕生於2003年，不同於一般的網路論壇，網友只要根據關鍵詞，就可自建一個貼吧，全盛時期號稱有高達15億網民，使用超過2272萬個吧群。<br />\n<br />\n著名的小說「盜墓筆記」，也誕生於百度貼吧。而2016年曾翻牆「洗版」蔡英文臉書的中國網民們，就是百度第一大貼吧「李毅吧」（又稱「帝吧」）的成員，粉絲數多達3100萬人。<br />\n<br />\n但貼吧的發展過程也遭遇重重問題。報導指出，為了解決營收困難，百度貼吧開始結合廣告，甚至把疾病類的吧群出售給醫院經營；2016年的「魏則西事件」事件，才讓整件事被披露出來。<br />\n<br />\n此外，百度在管理貼吧上，也數度與網民發生衝突。報導表示，百度曾經給志願性質的吧主（群組管理員）設定績效制度，不達標就撤換。<br />\n<br />\n還曾無預警地關閉文學性質貼吧，刪除網友原創作品。而這次隱藏2017年以前的貼文，報導形容「那幾乎是中國網民15年的歷史」。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，貼吧的的核心問題，在於百度公司的價值觀。百度公司董事長李彥宏對於隱私權的漠視，和對競價排名的堅持，將百度打造成「披著科技外衣的網絡營銷公司」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/201905270203.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F201905270203.aspx&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWB0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=faf9fc3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/201905270203.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"af3e9423d643a2a36079fd019ba33e2ecca695b5","tid":1173844,"uid":11148,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T11:48:12.000Z","msg":"網上焚書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48d7eaa0cb7587c6b10fb891ccfac1e34d3da5f2","tid":1173844,"uid":162783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T11:48:35.000Z","msg":"cls chi na"},{"pid":"c6d57b6909f9fde4f9221c3dac41eb50de8e600e","tid":1173844,"uid":50457,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T11:49:52.000Z","msg":"焚書坑儒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4650105a5e5c68f3aae241392a5d4205e74da13","tid":1173844,"uid":8219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T11:50:20.000Z","msg":"最大內聯網<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebb3e2de4dd4d58cbdb4a5f8bc4a2066fb5fd2c","tid":1173844,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"Details <br />\n<a href=\"https://chinaqna.com/a/82722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinaqna.com%2Fa%2F82722&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWB0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=11b3544f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinaqna.com/a/82722</a>"},{"pid":"7543b69381c121c3ae2b613b321457608b0e56f0","tid":1173844,"uid":237015,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T11:51:40.000Z","msg":"cls國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2019年仲做緊同秦朝一樣嘅事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5077914ab1164fed7f6780256305db1be22586","tid":1173844,"uid":15564,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T11:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/16/Repetitive_error.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20070902105305\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F16%2FRepetitive_error.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20070902105305&h=b7a3ba40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86aa7b483e90094a48fa4b6dc8b31df3b738b95e","tid":1173844,"uid":158504,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"垃圾網<br />\nWFC"},{"pid":"dc861c579bb447ac8ec37396f974ecec3f44dba7","tid"